General.Name: Jayex Technology Ltd
General.Description: Jayex Technology Limited provides healthcare industry service technologies in Australia and the United Kingdom. It offers Jayex Connect, a patient engagement platform that offers tools to manage patient experience and engagement comprising APPOINTUIT for online appointment booking; DISPLAY for transforming waiting room with digital displays; ARRIVE for patient self-check-in; and Jayex Survey that provides a toolkit for designing and publishing custom patient questionnaires. The company was formerly known as Jayex Healthcare Limited and changed its name to Jayex Technology Limited in May 2021. Jayex Technology Limited was founded in 1978 and is based in Milton, Australia.
